<h2>‚≠ê Use Loops and Randomness</h2>
<p>Draw many rectangles with a loop. Play with random sizes, positions or colors.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre><code class="language-evy">y := 5
while y &lt; 95
    move 2 y
    rect (rand1)*y 4
    y = y + 5
end
</code></pre>
